@startuml
title AIOps Codex 项目简单架构图（当前实现）

left to right direction
!theme plain

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundCorner 8
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam defaultFontName "Microsoft YaHei"

actor "用户" as User

rectangle "浏览器\nWeb UI" as Browser

node "本机" as LocalHost {
  package "ai-server（Go 进程）" as AIServer {
    component "HTTP API / WebSocket\n前后端入口" as API
    component "Session Store\n会话 / 卡片 / 运行态" as SessionStore
    component "Remote Gateway\nterminal / exec / files / approvals" as RemoteGateway
    component "Codex Client\nstdio JSON-RPC 客户端" as CodexClient
  }

  component "codex app-server\n子进程" as CodexApp
}

node "受控主机" as ManagedHosts {
  component "host-agent" as HostAgent
  component "Shell / Files / Terminal" as HostRuntime
}

cloud "OpenAI / ChatGPT" as OpenAI

User --> Browser : 请求
Browser --> API : 请求

API --> SessionStore : 读写会话状态
API --> Orchestrator : 创建 / 推进 mission
Orchestrator --> SessionStore : 回投摘要与任务状态
API --> RemoteGateway : 终端
API --> CodexClient : chat / tool calls

CodexClient --> CodexApp : stdio JSON-RPC
CodexApp --> OpenAI : 模型推理

RemoteGateway <-- HostAgent : gRPC 长连接
HostAgent --> HostRuntime : 操作

note bottom of AIServer
ai-server 是当前系统的统一入口：
- 提供前端 API / WebSocket
- 管理会话与审批
- 内嵌 orchestrator
- 拉起并连接 codex app-server
end note


@enduml
